title: L2 norm / Euclidean norm of a vector
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Consider a vector $$\bold{x}$$ in $$\reals^n$$ with elements $$\bold{x} = (x_1, x_2, ...x_n)$$ then:

$$
||\bold{x}||_2 = \sqrt{\sum_{i=1}^n x_i^2}
$$

